                     <hi rend="italic">of receiving. Judgment Respited.</hi>
                  </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">ADJOURNED TO MONDAY, SEPTEMBER</hi> 22<hi rend="smallCaps">ND</hi>, 1873.</p>
